    Subclasses of Space in thatslife 
    Modifier and Type Class Description
    class  BlueSpace
    This space inherits from the Space class and prompts the user to draw a BlueCard, upon playerLand.
    class  EndSpace
    This class defines the final space that players will land on, which is the retirement space.
    class  GreenSpace
    This class represents the space for Pay Day or Pay Raise.
    class  JunctionSpace
    This class defines the JunctionSpace, which is a MagentaSpace that prompts the user to decide where to go.
    class  MagentaSpace
    This class defines MagentaSpace, a type of space that requires the player to stop moving and execute its events.
    class  OrangeSpace
    This class defines the most common space in the game, the OrangeSpace.
    class  StartSpace
    This class defines the StartSpace, the starting point (insertion point) of all players in the game.
